{"tid":2181523,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［含劇透］頭先同阿仔玩 PS4 A Way Out爆咗機，佢喊咗成個鐘......","createTime":"2020-08-30T15:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T06:11:41.000Z","uid":28938,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bce5e757d74507f2dcde12898656646818d305ee","tid":2181523,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"趁大家都放假，呢幾日同仔仔一齊玩a way out，玩咗三日，兩仔爺今晚去到爆機最後階段。<br />\n<br />\n最後作為臥底嘅我要同個仔對打，但係我唔忍心打佢，所以一路放水，最後我個仔一拳打低咗我之後，佢就開始喊......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最慘係End Game嗰時仲要replay返我哋之前嘅合作，佢越睇喊得越犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：仔仔5歲，而家我俾佢老母質問緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早知玩on9 fall guys跳下跳下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9dceca5c9fd309e4a846d3ccf58a82298aa0cf","tid":2181523,"uid":235174,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"咁細個就識玩a way out?重要識睇劇情同喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136294a86e83f4250e82fb8d0a5cf88960fd16cd","tid":2181523,"uid":56657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"又製造左童年陰影俾仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bfbcbe15cd16d3bd4bcac76b68d30acd550e84","tid":2181523,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d9dceca5c9fd309e4a846d3ccf58a82298aa0cf","tid":2181523,"uid":235174,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"咁細個就識玩a way out?重要識睇劇情同喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"佢老竇一路玩一路解說俾佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4206a6b76a4d926f217dadf7abbc3e9e37ad35a6","tid":2181523,"uid":28938,"like":24,"dislike":1,"sco